.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: hip-hop, r&b, jazz, funk, house
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
City: san-francisco, liverpool, prague, paris, edinburgh

1. the fan of hip-hop is the person who likes red
2. the fan of r&b is the person traveling to san-francisco
3. the person drinking coffee is the person who likes green
4. the fan of jazz is the person drinking tea
5. the person who likes green is to the right of the person who likes ivory
6. the old-gold-smoker is the person traveling to edinburgh
7. the kools-smoker is the person who likes yellow
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the fan of funk is on the far left
10. the chesterfields-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool
11. the kools-smoker is to the left or right of the person traveling to paris
12. the lucky-strike-smoker is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the fan of house is the parliaments-smoker
14. the fan of funk is to the left or right of the person who likes blue

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Music-Genre	|   funk	|    jazz	|     hip-hop	|    r&b	|    house	|
| Color		|    yellow	|      blue	|      red	|     ivory	|     green	|
| Beverage	|     water	|      tea	|      milk	| orange-juice	|     coffee	|
| Cigar		|     kools	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| lucky-strike	|   parliament	|
| City		|     liverpool	|     paris	|     edinburgh	|     san-francisco	|     prague	|
